text: Henrietta is a city in the U.S. state of Texas. It is the county seat of Clay County. == History == Henrietta was created in 1874. == Geography == Henrietta has a total area of 5.2 square miles. == People == Henrietta has 3,111 people living there. == Well-known people == * Charlene Arthur Category:Cities in Texas Category:County seats in Texas
title: Henrietta, Texas
